{"tid":1243992,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［形象宣傳］不如搞老人院探訪團","createTime":"2019-06-19T16:43:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T03:02:19.000Z","uid":69419,"like":85,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9114baf78f1858a12e073b1c43d9c960e3475caa","tid":1243992,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:43:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1243678\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1243678</a><br />\n見到呢個post先醒起老人家既重要性<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢地老啦，出唔工黎抗爭。有D就讀得書少，唔明我地既志願。<br />\n<br />\n不過佢地都係公民，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">都有投票權！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，我建議舉行《連登乖孫暖萬心》既老人院循遊探訪。<br />\n<br />\n作為後生仔同老友記們傾下偈，交流下武功心得（掌心雷應對技巧），甚至細說點為下一代出多一分力。<br />\n<br />\n我而家都係構思階段。有冇社福界巴絲同一眾part time 乖孫一齊傾下點做？"},{"pid":"bd7635c9528f10031d45810830c8dff6b7b18197","tid":1243992,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:45:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"14365432847ef3fa62bc229f690a3d940eba6386","tid":1243992,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fb135d9fae1a0f987c24c86a997c5353e9d99d","tid":1243992,"uid":138173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:49:48.000Z","msg":"有人搞我會join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d8ecdab6e5b165d858c3bc4f26d9d053558545","tid":1243992,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T16:51:06.000Z","msg":"想參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5106abaa59df0c8794bcb08c4411d4679a9a6e","tid":1243992,"uid":4239,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0